  "text": "Cumulative exergy power input and output of the main propulsion turbine at different propulsion propeller speeds, calculated by using equations (11) and [CITATION_1] are presented in Fig.  3 . Main turbine cumulative exergy power input and output increases during the increase in propulsion propeller speed (increase in steam system load). The difference between main turbine cumulative exergy power input and output also increases during the increase in propulsion propeller speed, what defines main turbine exergy power losses (exergy destruction).",
